{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/improving-the-codesandbox-community","webpackCompilationHash":"43a07f76784e304bf1a0","result":{"data":{"blogPost":{"fields":{"authors":["Ives van Hoorne"],"date":"2018-12-19T00:00:00.000Z","description":"It's time for a new update to CodeSandbox! This time we focused on the most important part of CodeSandbox: the community.","photo":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/587016?s=460&v=4","slug":"improving-the-codesandbox-community","title":"Improving the CodeSandbox Community"},"frontmatter":{"banner":{"publicURL":"/static/banner-0528d0c8b0925c461d45d7f474109ffc.png"}},"html":"<p>It's time for a new update to <a href=\"https://codesandbox.io\">CodeSandbox</a>! This time\nwe focused on the most important part of CodeSandbox: the community. Without a\ncommunity, CodeSandbox would not be the platform it would be today, and it\ndefinitely deserves some more love.</p>\n<p>We did three things to make it easier for everyone to find and share sandboxes.\nLet's get to it!</p>\n<section>\n<h2 id=\"explore-page\"><a href=\"#explore-page\" aria-label=\"explore page permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Explore Page</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 740px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/ccc27/0.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.05729166666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"0\"\n        title=\"0\"\n        src=\"/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/bcf2d/0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/d5c4a/0.png 185w,\n/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/04e89/0.png 370w,\n/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/bcf2d/0.png 740w,\n/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/dbb75/0.png 1110w,\n/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/a808b/0.png 1480w,\n/static/532fae1042ac933e87c02add826b9add/ccc27/0.png 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>CodeSandbox always strove to make itself the best way to create experiments and\nto prototype apps, but until now there was no way to see the experiments unless\nyou found the perfect <a href=\"https://twitter.com\">Twitter</a> thread. While working on\nCodeSandbox we found so many hidden gems, and we feel like we should bring them\nmore to light.</p>\n<p>That's why we're happy to announce the\n<a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/explore\">explore page</a>! A page with hand-picked\nsandboxes which we deem either interesting, beautiful or both! We have invited a\ngroup of curators who can pick sandboxes that go on the explore page. We\nconstantly pick new sandboxes for the explore page.</p>\n<p>Please send us all your cool sandboxes by tweeting with a mention to\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/codesandbox\">@codesandbox</a>, so we can feature you on the\nexplore page!</p>\n<p><em>We created a documentation entry with answers to some questions about the\nexplore page <a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/docs/explore\">here</a>.</em></p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<h2 id=\"move-to-spectrum\"><a href=\"#move-to-spectrum\" aria-label=\"move to spectrum permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Move to Spectrum</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 740px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/e1ff9/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.57519788918205%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/bcf2d/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/d5c4a/1.png 185w,\n/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/04e89/1.png 370w,\n/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/bcf2d/1.png 740w,\n/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/dbb75/1.png 1110w,\n/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/a808b/1.png 1480w,\n/static/bc4ace9aa91707c3c592e5324f3cddc3/e1ff9/1.png 1516w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>We've always been using <a href=\"https://discordapp.com\">Discord</a> for communication with\nthe community. As the popularity of CodeSandbox grew we started to notice that\nit was hard for everyone to keep up with all the chatter. Furthermore, we\nreceived many duplicate questions that were answered before.</p>\n<p>We've seen so many amazing things happen at <a href=\"https://spectrum.chat\">Spectrum</a>\nthat we made the decision to move our community there. Spectrum solves all the\nissues that we had by giving a thread based conversation model, another big plus\nis that everything is searchable from search engines!</p>\n<p>This will make it easier to ask questions and to share your ideas and work! If\nyou want to be a part of it\n<a href=\"https://spectrum.chat/codesandbox\">you can join it here</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<h2 id=\"submit-feedback\"><a href=\"#submit-feedback\" aria-label=\"submit feedback permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Submit Feedback</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 740px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/2f950/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/bcf2d/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/d5c4a/2.png 185w,\n/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/04e89/2.png 370w,\n/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/bcf2d/2.png 740w,\n/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/dbb75/2.png 1110w,\n/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/a808b/2.png 1480w,\n/static/9e32c6bf0b8f17fe843dbb8c06f2772b/2f950/2.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The 'Submit Feedback' button is back! If you have any ideas for a new feature,\nor you just want to let us know your thoughts, you can do that now from the user\nmenu. We'll stay on top of all the feedback.</p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<h2 id=\"the-future-of-the-community-in-codesandbox\"><a href=\"#the-future-of-the-community-in-codesandbox\" aria-label=\"the future of the community in codesandbox permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The future of the community in CodeSandbox</h2>\n<p>That's where all of you enter and get to join this discussion to help us better\nshape the community we are trying to create. Join our\n<a href=\"https://spectrum.chat/codesandbox\">Spectrum</a> and tell us your ideas. We all\nhave valuable ideas that can make CodeSandbox better and better every day.</p>\n<p>Let us know for what you use it and what is missing and we can all build this\ncommunity together and make it better!</p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<h2 id=\"thank-you\"><a href=\"#thank-you\" aria-label=\"thank you permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Thank you</h2>\n<p>Thanks to everyone working on this update. A special thanks to\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NikkitaFTW\">Sara Vieira</a> for putting an incredible amount\nof effort in this update, she did an incredible job in making this happen.</p>\n<p>Also thanks to you! Without your sandboxes we wouldn't have anything to put on\nthe explore page to begin with!</p>\n</section>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cb2df4e6-2fc0-5bc3-a8f6-caf9c5ea33e1"}}}